Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.17,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Caution... Fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:14.91,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You hold your breath to make it through\Nthe bewildering day that confronts you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:21.09,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what this is, don't you?\NWhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:27.68,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain from shrugging\Nit all off as nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:33.60,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,urges you on enough to be encouraging
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:40.15,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Catching hold but making a mess,\Nwe're still inadequate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:48.18,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but as long as we can forge\Nour shining, unseen future selves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:56.62,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken and run where it takes you,\Nleaving mirages behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:03.17,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Run with your desire to change,\Nfrom your comfort zone into freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:10.60,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start choosing between now\Nand the brilliance you can attain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:18.63,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Unaware of your destination,\Ndeep breaths following shallow ones
