Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.80,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chi-chan and Oreki are already here.\NCome to the office and wait."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:44.66,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Change made"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.92,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bowls
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.33,0:24:26.33,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation is an unscientific\Nmontage of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.96,0:24:29.60,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is calling whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.63,0:24:35.52,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Your gaze darts away when I turn around\N(I can feel it)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.55,0:24:37.82,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unkind to tell me I'm imagining things
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.85,0:24:43.32,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They say having\Nantennas is a talent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.35,0:24:48.41,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean I want to know\N(I mean) (don't you?)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.44,0:24:55.21,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn up the heat on your youth\Nfor you now, while there's time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.24,0:24:59.88,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can solve this tomorrow,\Nwhy not solve it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.91,0:25:05.47,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to solve your mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:10.18,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Track down that secretive boyish figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.21,0:25:17.77,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Today) you are a fantasy,\Ndrawing me to you, no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.80,0:25:23.32,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My curiosity is expanding,\Nlack of tricks notwithstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.35,0:25:30.32,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fascinated, and I have to know, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.07,0:25:40.99,SignsT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,204)}The Case of the Homemade Chocolates
